This new zero version of our famous Virgil's Rood Beer is naturally sweetened with Stevie,an all natural,zero calorie sweetener affectionately called Sweetleaf. In Japan,Stevia accounts for 40 of the sweeteners consumed. Most Stevia sodas also use sugar alcohol as such as erythritol to sweeten their product. Virgil's contains Zero sugar alcohol.
